    "description": {
      "content": "Cloudflare AI Gateway provides visibility and control over AI applications with analytics, logging, caching, rate limiting, request retries, and model fallback. It supports multiple AI providers including OpenAI, Anthropic, and Google Gemini through a unified interface. The API allows developers to create and manage gateways, configure providers, and access logs and analytics.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Cloudflare Support",
